{"tid":2186960,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"補習天王跳槽被索償千一萬","createTime":"2020-09-03T10:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T13:59:23.000Z","uid":57405,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0eb7dcdca86b40b0e1aaae73e0833ce40ec4c3","tid":2186960,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:23:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20060609/RGQHCWN35UAEKQEPFKUTSYV3XI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20060609%2FRGQHCWN35UAEKQEPFKUTSYV3XI%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=f4ad1f74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20060609%2FRGQHCWN35UAEKQEPFKUTSYV3XI%2F&h=1f734447\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20060609/RGQHCWN35UAEKQEPFKUTSYV3XI/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QXg_2ipydFdoGHYz-WmOjHU4mJc=/802x514/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2PSJW7DKVHPEOXXSNENFEH6PYI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQXg_2ipydFdoGHYz-WmOjHU4mJc%3D%2F802x514%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2PSJW7DKVHPEOXXSNENFEH6PYI.jpg&h=258f64de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">補習天王DickHui（左二）跳槽現代教育，被前僱主英皇教育入稟追討逾千萬元賠償。&lt;BR&gt;壹週刊資料圖片</span><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】曾於英皇教育中心任教數學科的補習天王DickHui，早前高調表示將跳槽到現代教育任教。英皇教育昨日入稟高等法院，指DickHui突然離職違反雙方早前簽訂的合約，除向法庭申請禁制令，禁止他在其他補習學校任教外，更向在英皇每月平均收入近50萬元的他追討逾1100萬元損失。現代教育則表示DickHui會如期於7月開班。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"large\">每月入息49萬元</span></strong></span><br />\n原訴人為英皇教育中心及另外6間姊妹公司，被告則為前僱員DickHui，英皇教育昨以事件已交律師處理，拒絕作出回應。現代教育發言人則表示DickHui並無與英皇教育簽訂合約，他將如期在7月到現代任教，並強調任何情況下學生均可在上課前無條件全數退回學費。<br />\n入稟狀顯示，被告與英皇教育於03年7月簽訂五年合約，除訂明雙方以六四分賬瓜分由被告開班所得的收入外，亦提及雙方如中止合約，必須有兩年通知期，而被告離職後一年內不可以任何方式在其他補習學校任教。<br />\n被告於上月23日以電郵通知英皇教育，他將於6月學期完結後離職，並於兩天後再以書信交代離職事宜。他於本月3日在報章及電台透過廣告宣布跳槽現代教育，該校的網頁在6月4日將被告加入「星級名師」之列。<br />\n根據英皇教育計算，被告於去年5月至今年5月在分得補習班總收入的6成後，平均每月入息為49萬多元。由於被告是次離職，令英皇教育在未來兩年至少損失1100多萬元，更需退還近15萬元予報讀被告補習班的學生，故入稟法院索償及禁止被告在本月6日起的一年內，在任何補習學校任教。<br />\n資料顯示，曾為會考狀元的DickHui上月曾於網上留言，表明不滿公司及支持「兄弟」，決定離開。他的學生均相信所指的「兄弟」，是早前因與英皇教育就拆賬興訟的英皇英文科「補習天王」范奧天（K.Oten）。他們兩人曾於旺角開設食肆。<br />\n案件編號：HCA1225/06"},{"pid":"32048ec118d0fa3b3886c98a9521dcf5e67baec3","tid":2186960,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:23:55.000Z","msg":"而家Dick Hui咪又死死地氣返英皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab4232bd7863017fba31ca89db12ec48090af86","tid":2186960,"uid":118754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:57:39.000Z","msg":"ken chan <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0cdd509bb69989684b5f4ed3582917e554ff55","tid":2186960,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:25:26.000Z","msg":"K.O. Ten"},{"pid":"1c6c39cf31ac4b9ed80f0f84447852006d34b6a6","tid":2186960,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:26:21.000Z","msg":"相入面既天王已經冇再教"},{"pid":"ee01efab7cf6c81434337561c6c8ebdabe68ce2e","tid":2186960,"uid":135445,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:29:05.000Z","msg":"2006年你擺上黎把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e724578459b62d4376418abbc97f6c7b0cb87784","tid":2186960,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:31:10.000Z","msg":"Duck hui又返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c661a9f85e598729d76b4db9b61099b21807413","tid":2186960,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee01efab7cf6c81434337561c6c8ebdabe68ce2e","tid":2186960,"uid":135445,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:29:05.000Z","msg":"2006年你擺上黎把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"當年KO ten、Dick Hui、周勤才同英皇搞到咁疆，而家KOten同周勤才唔做補習，得返Dick hui一個留係補習界。<br />\n真係好想知佢睇返呢單新聞會有咩感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7722ab3ae7bb7091c0b68f6ae1bbf75126a99d","tid":2186960,"uid":57405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:35:15.000Z","msg":"以前補過佢M1，認真屈機<br />\n不過有朋友補佢M2佢真係麻麻"},{"pid":"6b19bf82193c44a442d84275067729822b796794","tid":2186960,"uid":185415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:45:24.000Z","msg":"原來搵咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e71955065815f21061a9a402392347af25f9696","tid":2186960,"uid":118754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b19bf82193c44a442d84275067729822b796794","tid":2186960,"uid":185415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:45:24.000Z","msg":"原來搵咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"06年呀<br />\n當年ce+al咁多考生<br />\n差唔多啦"},{"pid":"e1f2644157b6565746de21e246e39b8a4afed5e1","tid":2186960,"uid":269020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:55:50.000Z","msg":"仲有補習天王？ 吓"},{"pid":"aaff014ccefc6de299923e992b2668ec5693d530","tid":2186960,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c6c39cf31ac4b9ed80f0f84447852006d34b6a6","tid":2186960,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:26:21.000Z","msg":"相入面既天王已經冇再教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:59:10.000Z","msg":"kevin ko全盛期退落黎去做傢俬佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2596b0c7b580313b93e6